Hey, everyone! My name is Sam Tsui and I’m a singer, actor, songwriter, (and college student) who simply loves to make music. Whether I’m jamming out at the piano, performing a musical, recording a cover on YouTube, or belting in the shower, being able to share something I have so much fun doing makes me incredibly happy! I’ve recently started recording a bunch of covers and videos with my friend Kurt, which you can now listen to (and hopefully enjoy!) here on my Myspace

You should also check out Kurt (www.myspace.com/KurtHugo) - he’s an incredibly talented songwriter, musician, and producer, and the mastermind behind all of my recordings and videos. 

This summer, in addition to continuing to record covers, I also plan to start working on some original music of mine or of Kurt’s, so keep an eye out for that – Hopefully at some point you’ll be seeing a full album! 

Thanks for your support - Friend me and say hi… I’d love to get to know everyone who’s out there listening! And if you like my music, download and tell your friends! 

Sam
